<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>321</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ yī guì xià jiù kū le, qí qiú nǐ bǎo shǒu jiào huì,
 bǎo shǒu nǐ de pū rén, píng píng ān ān shēng cún tuō lí mái fú zhī rén,
 wǒ qí dǎo de shuāng shǒu, méi yǒu xiǎng dào shōu huí, qiú nǐ shè zuì lián mǐn,
 yǐn dǎo tā men zǒu lù, cì gěi tā men yī kē yǒng bù tuì hòu de xīn.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ wǒ yī guì xià 迦南321</title>
</song>